    "cnSpeaker": "",
    "enSpeaker": "",
    "Location": "",
    "cnAction": "",
    "cnWords": "*[旁白]*\n沉默了一会儿。\n走廊里有别处的脚步声，很远，很轻。\nVivian 没有说\"谢谢\"，也没有说\"不用\"。",
    "enAction": "",
    "enWords": "",
    "next": "806004012",
    "script": "",
    "ParameterStr0": "",
    "ParameterStr1": "",
    "ParameterStr2": "",
    "ParameterInt0": 0,
    "ParameterInt1": 0,
    "ParameterInt2": 0,
    "videoEpisode": "EPI08",
    "videoLoop": "loop6",
    "videoId": "806004011",
    "videoScene": "vivian_004"
  },
  {
    "id": 806004012,
    "step": 12,
    "speakType": 4,
    "waitTime": 0,
    "IdSpeaker": "",
    "cnSpeaker": "",
    "enSpeaker": "",
    "Location": "",
    "cnAction": "",
    "cnWords": "\"还有一件事没有做完。\"\n*[触发 Act 3 场景切换]*",
    "enAction": "",
    "enWords": "",
    "next": "806005001",
